BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Anti-Fascist Craft Night in Lititz with the Warwick Democrats!
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260401T220000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260402T000000Z
UID:d9f5ce8e218895d2992b111553bb7626@mobilize.us
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mobilize-uploads-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/u
 ploads/event/anti-facist_craft_night_20250731134502634757.jpg
DESCRIPTION:We love democracy. We love crafts. We love snacks. And we love
  civic engagement. You too? Join us for **Anti-Fascist Craft Night** in Li
 titz—a low-key hang where we cut up cereal boxes and old magazines\, mak
 e wild collage postcards and letters\, and send our thoughts (and shade) t
 o our elected officials. Make your voice heard in a weirdly therapeutic an
 d hands-on way! **What to bring:** * Clean cardboard (cereal/snack boxes) 
 or card stock * Old magazines\, catalogs\, newspapers\, greeting cards\, e
 tc
LOCATION:Lititz\, PA
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/lancastercountydems/event/821867/
X-SOURCE:Lancaster County Dems (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
